---
// 把这个文件的内容复制到 src/pages/index.astro
---

<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>张伟 · 全栈开发工程师</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0e0e0e;
      --surface: #161616;
      --border: #2a2a2a;
      --text: #e8e8e8;
      --muted: #888;
      --accent: #7c6ff7;
      --accent2: #5dcaa5;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── 导航 ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(14,14,14,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .logo { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent2);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--accent2);
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 .highlight { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all .2s;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #6a5fe0; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── 通用 Section ── */
    section {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    /* ── 技能 ── */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .skill-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .skill-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
    .skill-card h3 { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
    .tag {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: #1e1e1e;
      color: var(--muted);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    /* ── 经历 ── */
    .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .tl-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .tl-date { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); padding-top: 4px; }
    .tl-content h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .tl-content .company { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .tl-content p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── 项目 ── */
    .projects-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .project-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .project-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .project-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .project-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .project-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
    .project-link { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; margin-top: 1rem; display: inline-block; }
    .project-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── 联系 ── */
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .contact-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .contact-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent2); }
    .contact-card .icon { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .contact-card .label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .contact-card .value { font-size: 0.9rem; }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .tl-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.25rem; }
      .tl-date { padding-top: 0; }
      nav { padding: 1rem; }
      .nav-links { gap: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- 导航 -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">张<span>.</span>伟</div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#skills">技能</a></li>
      <li><a href="#experience">经历</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects">项目</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">联系</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <span class="badge">可接受新机会</span>
    <h1>你好，我是<br /><span class="highlight">张伟</span></h1>
    <p>全栈开发工程师，专注于构建高性能 Web 应用。热爱开源，喜欢用代码解决实际问题。</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">查看项目</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">联系我</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 技能 -->
  <section id="skills">
    <p class="section-label">专业技能</p>
    <h2>我能做什么</h2>
    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>前端</h3>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span>
          <span class="tag">Vue</span>
          <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="tag">Astro</span>
          <span class="tag">TailwindCSS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>后端</h3>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
          <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="tag">Redis</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card">
        <h3>工具 & 其他</h3>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">Git</span>
          <span class="tag">Docker</span>
          <span class="tag">Linux</span>
          <span class="tag">GitHub Actions</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 经历 -->
  <section id="experience">
    <p class="section-label">工作经历</p>
    <h2>我做过什么</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-date">2023 — 至今</div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3>高级前端工程师</h3>
          <div class="company">某科技有限公司</div>
          <p>负责核心产品前端架构设计，主导组件库建设，将页面加载速度提升 40%。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-date">2021 — 2023</div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3>全栈开发工程师</h3>
          <div class="company">某互联网公司</div>
          <p>负责后台管理系统的全栈开发，独立完成从需求分析到上线部署的全流程。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-date">2017 — 2021</div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3>计算机科学与技术 · 本科</h3>
          <div class="company">某大学</div>
          <p>GPA 3.8 / 4.0，获优秀毕业生称号。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 项目 -->
  <section id="projects">
    <p class="section-label">项目作品</p>
    <h2>我做过的项目</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>个人博客系统</h3>
        <p>基于 Astro + MDX 构建的静态博客，支持暗色模式和 RSS 订阅，部署在 GitHub Pages。</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="tag">Astro</span>
          <span class="tag">MDX</span>
          <span class="tag">TailwindCSS</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="project-link">查看源码 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>任务管理 App</h3>
        <p>全栈任务管理应用，前端 React，后端 FastAPI，支持多人协作和实时同步。</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span>
          <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="project-link">查看源码 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>CLI 工具集</h3>
        <p>一组提升开发效率的命令行工具，Python 编写，发布在 PyPI，超过 500 次下载。</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">Click</span>
          <span class="tag">PyPI</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="project-link">查看源码 →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <h3>论文标题</h3>
        <p>发表于 某期刊 / 某会议 · 2024</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="tag">关键词一</span>
          <span class="tag">关键词二</span>
          <span class="tag">关键词三</span>
        </div>
        <a href="你的论文链接或/paper.pdf" class="project-link">查看论文 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 联系 -->
  <section id="contact">
    <p class="section-label">保持联系</p>
    <h2>找到我</h2>
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="contact-card">
        <div class="icon">✉</div>
        <div class="label">邮箱</div>
        <div class="value">your@email.com</div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" class="contact-card">
        <div class="icon">⌥</div>
        <div class="label">GitHub</div>
        <div class="value">@yourusername</div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com" class="contact-card">
        <div class="icon">in</div>
        <div class="label">LinkedIn</div>
        <div class="value">张伟</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 张伟 · 用 Astro 构建</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>